      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a highly reliable daily driver for anyone looking for dependable transportation. While it remains mechanically sound, please note that it shows clear signs of age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. It has been regularly serviced, making it a solid choice for someone who prioritizes utility and performance over a perfect aesthetic.",
