      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one, and it's ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
