    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint maintains its deep luster with no swirl marks or imperfections. A true purist\u2019s specimen with a linear power band and surgical steering precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
